---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Maine Dispensary Packaging & Labeling | Maine Dispensary Guide" description="Complete guide to cannabis packaging and labeling requirements in Maine. Child-resistant packaging, labeling laws, and compliance.">
  <article>
    <header>
      <h1>Packaging & Labeling Requirements</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Understanding Maine's cannabis packaging and labeling regulations</p>
    </header>

    <section>
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>Maine has strict packaging and labeling requirements designed to protect consumers, prevent accidental ingestion, and ensure product safety. Compliance is mandatory and enforced by the Maine Office of Cannabis Policy.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Packaging Requirements</h2>
      
      <h3>Child-Resistant Packaging</h3>
      <p>All cannabis products must be sold in child-resistant packaging that meets federal ASTM standards.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Push-and-turn containers</li>
        <li>Squeeze-and-turn containers</li>
        <li>Other certified child-resistant mechanisms</li>
        <li>Reclosable packages must remain child-resistant after opening</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Appearance Restrictions</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Packaging cannot resemble candy or soda</li>
        <li>No bright, attractive colors that appeal to children</li>
        <li>No cartoon characters or child-friendly imagery</li>
        <li>No misleading claims about effects</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Labeling Requirements</h2>
      <p>All cannabis products must include specific information on the label:</p>
      
      <h3>Mandatory Information:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Product name and description</li>
        <li>THC content (total and per serving)</li>
        <li>CBD content</li>
        <li>Net weight or volume</li>
        <li>Ingredients list</li>
        <li>Allergen information</li>
        <li>Manufacturer/producer name and license number</li>
        <li>Production date</li>
        <li>Expiration date (if applicable)</li>
        <li>Unique identifier / batch number</li>
        <li>Required warnings</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Required Warnings:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>"Keep out of reach of children"</li>
        <li>"For use only by adults 21+ or qualified patients"</li>
        <li>Pregnancy warning</li>
        <li>Impairment warning</li>
        <li>Storage instructions</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Testing & Certification</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>All products must be tested by a licensed Maine laboratory</li>
        <li>Testing required for potency, contaminants, pesticides</li>
        <li>Test results must be available to consumers</li>
        <li>Failed products cannot be sold</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Packaging Materials</h2>
      <p>Source packaging from approved suppliers:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Child-resistant containers</li>
        <li>Exit bags</li>
        <li>Jars and bottles</li>
        <li>Pre-roll tubes</li>
        <li>Edible packaging</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Compliance Tips</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Verify all suppliers meet Maine requirements</li>
        <li>Train staff on packaging protocols</li>
        <li>Inspect all incoming products</li>
        <li>Maintain proper storage conditions</li>
        <li>Document all compliance procedures</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Key Takeaways</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Child-resistant packaging is mandatory</li>
        <li>No child-friendly packaging or marketing</li>
        <li>Detailed labeling required</li>
        <li>Laboratory testing required before sale</li>
        <li>Source from approved suppliers</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="disclaimer">
      <p><em>Requirements subject to change. Verify current Maine OCP requirements.</em></p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  article { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
  header { margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .subtitle { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-text-light); }
  section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section h2, section h3 { margin-top: 1.5rem; }
  section h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  section h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; }
  ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .disclaimer { background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffc107; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; }
</style>
